    {
        "url": "/quotes/alan_cooper_725626",
        "quote": "There's a fundamental problem with how the software business does things. We're asking people who are masters of hard-edged technology to design the soft, human side of software as well. As a result, they make products that are really cool - if you happen to be a software engineer.",
